(5, 'Md. Rakibul Bassar', 'rakibul.bassar.du@gmail.com', '01752066299', '96/4 Nazimuddin Road, Dhaka', 'May 03, 2021 \r\nRecruiting Manager\r\nMarriage Solution BD\r\nDhaka, Bangladesh\r\nSubject: An Application for the post of Public Relationship Officer\r\nDear Sir,\r\nI recently learned of the job opportunity with the Marriage Solution BD. In response to your published advertisement; I am writing to you in hopes of being considered for this role. I am a graduate of the University of Dhaka with a Bachelor of Arts in Persian Language and Literature. I am very familiar with your organization and I believe my work experience, skillset, and commitment will support your organization\'s mission.\r\nI have my English Language Course from the Institute of Modern Language-IML, University of Dhaka, and a database course from Arts Computer Center, University of Dhaka. I exercise high attention to detail to maintain accuracy and consistency in my performance, collaborative teamwork, and on-time completion of all projects. Moreover, I offer observation, teamwork, and scheduling flexibility.\r\nI would appreciate the opportunity to meet with you to find out more about this position and discuss my qualification. I am available for an interview at your convenience.\r\nSincerely,\r\nMd. Rakibul Bassar', 'storage/application/cv/ZCSK10py1620031987.pdf', 0, 0, 0, '2021-05-03 02:53:07', '2021-05-03 02:53:07'),
(6, 'Sonia Md. Abdus Sattar', 'Soniabipasha@gmail.com', '01753940813', 'House 376, Road 5, Block i, Basundhara R /A', 'Good morning Sir,\r\nThis is Sonia Md. Abdus Sattar. I found a job offer as \"Office Executive\" on bd jobs. I would like to apply for the position. Kindly look at my resume. Thank you', 'storage/application/cv/slux6Xei1620082320.pdf', 0, 0, 0, '2021-05-03 16:52:00', '2021-05-03 16:52:00'),
(7, 'Khadija Tanis Cauli', 'khadizatanis@gmail.com', '+8801855456399', 'Goribullah shah housing society', '04th May, 2021\r\nMarriage Solution Bd\r\nDear Sir/Madam,\r\n I am writing in response to your recent advertisement for the position of “office executive\" and other job post. I am really interested in working with ‘’ marriage solution bd\" to fulfill their need and learn some more for myself as well. \r\nI believe my Educational Background and Gathered experience from call center as a customer service associate in endowed me with the qualities that you are looking for. I have completed my four years Bachelor degree in Computer Science & Engineering (CSE) from Premier University Chittagong Bangladesh. My involvement in extra-curricular activities helped me build a know how attitude and a good interpersonal relationship with people of varied interest. I have actively Participated in many events and also Organized few in my University and outside as well. Also, I\'m focused ,determined and a multitasker. As a fresher my newness could be an asset to do work properly with determination. By giving a chance it\'ll be great opportunity for me to build up my career and confidence as a woman and fresher. I want to be a member of your company in chattogram branch.My CV enclosed here with will provide you further details. \r\nI would appreciate the opportunity to discuss my qualification with you. Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing from you.\r\n Sincerely \r\nKhadija Tanis Cauli', 'storage/application/cv/AcCXXh7a1620161615.docx', 0, 0, 0, '2021-05-04 14:53:36', '2021-05-04 14:53:36'),
(8, 'Apu Dabnath', 'apu.dabnath.ad@gmail.com', '01844468229', 'Moushair, Nagar Bari Road, Daskhinkhan, Dhaka-1230', 'Dear Sir / Madam,\r\n\r\nThank you for the opportunity to apply for the (Customer Service Executive) role at your company. After reviewing your job description, it\'s clear that you\'re looking for a candidate that is extremely familiar with the responsibilities associated with the role, and can perform them confidently. Given these requirements, I am certain that I have the necessary skills to successfully do the job adeptly and perform above expectations.\r\n\r\nI am a quality-oriented recent college graduate (Accounting) from Kanchkura University & College. During the course of my academic career, I also managed to accrue nearly 4.7 years of work experience. Currently I work at My Outsourcing Ltd as a Customer Service Executive. I had the privilege of working for Genex Infosys Limited in a BPO sector as a Customer Service Associate role in my free time, where I learned valuable professional skills such as customer Service, communications, issues resolved. I also worked in ACI Logistic LTD. As a Checkout Assistant (CA) & I had been working for Devnet LTD, As an Executive. In both my academic and professional life I have been consistently praised as results-oriented by my professors and peers. Whether working on academic, extracurricular, or professional projects, I apply proven communication, leadership and problem-solving skills, which I hope to leverage into the Issue Resolution role at your company.\r\n\r\nAfter reviewing my resume, I hope you will agree that I am the type of competent and competitive candidate you are looking for. I look forward to elaborating on how my specific skills and abilities will benefit your organization. Please contact me at +880-184-446-8229 or via email at apu.dabnath.ad@gmail.com to arrange for a convenient meeting time.\r\n\r\nThank you for your consideration, and I look forward to hearing from you soon.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nApu Dabnath\r\n\r\napu.dabnath.ad@gmail.com\r\nContact: +8801844468229', 'storage/application/cv/JL3JjTvR1620322102.pdf', 0, 0, 0, '2021-05-06 11:28:23', '2021-05-06 11:28:23'),
(9, 'M. Toushif Shadman Bejoy', 'tawsif_robin@yhaoo.com', '01712599212', '61, Omar Ali Lane, West Rampura, Dhaka-1219.', 'Dear Marriage Solution Bd,\r\n\r\nI have come to know that your reputed organisation is looking for \"Public Relationship Officer.\"\r\nI am a fresh graduate  from the University of Chittagong with a BSS in Public Administration. I am willing to put my knowledge and skills to work for your organisation. I am a fast learner and, I will do everything within my position to achieve the goal of your organisation. I have attached my curriculum vitae along with this application form for your persual. Please,  do not hesitate to reach out for further information. \r\nThank you for your time and kindness for this opportunity.  I am looking forward to hearing from you soon.\r\n\r\nYour Sincerely,\r\n\r\nM. Toushif Shadman Bejoy\r\ntawsif_robin@yahoi.com', 'storage/application/cv/DiDdHH3T1620412772.pdf', 0, 0, 0, '2021-05-07 12:39:34', '2021-05-07 12:39:34'),
